{
  "stem": "25348.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was very hard to get to America unless somebody guaranteed [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were different people, you know, like the people here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these people, they were relatives legally, but they've never met me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was born long after they left for the States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Had I persevered, perhaps I would have got away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I met my husband and we came to Australia in 1950.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came by-- by boat called",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Australia?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We arrived in-- originally in Sydney and then we went to Brisbane by some-- someone read the passenger list, and they thought that Brisbane would be easier for jobs.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as it appears, it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Though I secured a good job in Brisbane, I trained-- I made a crash course, kind of [INAUDIBLE] 12 months course in-- in Munich as a-- as a lab technician.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we were looking for skills that you could utilize as a migrant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I got myself a job at the Brisbane blood bank.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I have a photo there which will tell you that I was promoted from this lab job, staring into a microscope, counting-- doing blood counts, to a PR job.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They tried and-- you see, in Europe, blood is not donated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's being paid for.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they tried to move migrants to tell them, give them a message, that they are recipients of blood, but they're not donors.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was my task to do this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And from the photo that you have there, which I left with you, you'll find out that it was successful because we had queues of migrants.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was picked up by a doctor who looked like the migrant-- I don't remember the camp, but it was like a Victorian Bonegilla migrant.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
